---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Life of Our Leader Rabbi Nachman" description="The story of Rebbe Nachman's life by Rabbi Natan">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>The Life of Our Leader Rabbi Nachman</h1>
    <p>חיי מוהרן</p>
    <a href="/teachings" class="back-link">← Back to Teachings</a>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="description">
        <strong>The Life of Our Leader Rabbi Nachman</strong> (Chayei Moharan) is the foundational biography 
        of Rebbe Nachman written by his close disciple, Rabbi Natan. This work contains profound insights 
        into Rebbe Nachman's life, his conversations, his teachings, and the events that shaped his holy path.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Contents</h2>
      <div class="contents-list">
        <a href="/teachings/life-introduction" class="content-item">
          <span class="number">1</span>
          <div class="text">
            <h3>Introduction</h3>
            <p>Overview of Rebbe Nachman's life and mission</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/teachings/life-childhood" class="content-item">
          <span class="number">2</span>
          <div class="text">
            <h3>Childhood and Early Years</h3>
            <p>Rebbe Nachman's formative years</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/teachings/life-breslov" class="content-item">
          <span class="number">3</span>
          <div class="text">
            <h3>Years in Breslov</h3>
            <p>The center of the Breslov movement</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/teachings/life-uman" class="content-item">
          <span class="number">4</span>
          <div class="text">
            <h3>Journey to Uman</h3>
            <p>The final years and Rosh Hashanah gatherings</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/teachings/life-passing" class="content-item">
          <span class="number">5</span>
          <div class="text">
            <h3>Passing and Legacy</h3>
            <p>Rebbe Nachman's last days and enduring influence</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quote">
    <div class="container">
      <blockquote>
        <p class="hebrew">כל העולם כולו גשר צר מאד והעיקר לא לפחד כלל</p>
        <p>"The whole world is a very narrow bridge, and the main thing is not to fear at all."</p>
        <cite>— Rebbe Nachman of Breslov</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #744210 0%, #5d3a1a 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-hebrew);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid white;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .intro {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #f7f5f0;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .contents-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .content-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .content-item:hover {
    transform: translateX(8px);
  }

  .number {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .text h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .text p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .quote {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quote blockquote {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote .hebrew {
    font-family: var(--font-hebrew);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .quote p {
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
